During Pastor Doug’s time in Mandeville, Jamaica, he and the Amazing Facts Center of Evangelism team have also been training numerous souls in the art of outreach. This special series, called “Project Pentecost,” is equipping and energizing pastors, Bible workers, and laypeople to reach their communities for Christ with love, compassion, and healing.
